item.title: Vanity - Why? We are Superb
item.dc:creator: @Project-Storm Project-Storm
item.description:
@Project-Storm wrote:

[quote=“TinyDan, post:4, topic:550458”][quote author=Project-Storm link=topic=669366.msg4476104#msg4476104 date=1425984225]

I simply love when people take the time to copy some of my work. It might not be a big deal to others and might make me seem big-headed (not to mention what I feel proud about) but I take proud about how I formatted the sections and boards on the communities I’ve help built, and forums I’ve done simply because of how much time I took into consideration of each and every board. From you, the sections and boards were taken from Ikov (or at least another community that I put the sections and boards as such) because of what I took into consideration and how I made them. I also see you’ve copied Ikov’s veteran rank (don’t care for the others as they were not unique).

Anyway, like I said, it might not be a big deal to you or anyone else but it is to me as I am pretty OCD about organization, professionalism and what not but still, I like what I’ve done and do.

Good luck with the development nonetheless, the server looks decent and the theme looks meh… I’d suggest sometime making a custom theme for your forum. Also, vBulletin is barely used nowadays for some reasons that I’m not going to get into but I used to love it, I hate it now. Perhaps another like SMF, PHPBB, MyBB, or IPB? Either or, I wish for the best of luck.

His G.E is going to ruin his server lol…
[/quote]

If all you’re going to do is attempt to degrade me over a forums page then you can leave, thanks buddy.[/quote]

You have a staff of air bought for a bill, or sold for a bill… Stfu, noones degrading you but yourself by posting this…
IN the pictures, there’s shit THAT’S clearly not right, or good.
